  "metadata": {
    "event": "IEM Cologne Major 2026 Stage 1",
    "updated_at": "2026-05-26",
    "notes": [
      "参赛队伍参考 HLTV 的 IEM Cologne Major 2026 Stage 1 赛事页。",
      "seed 用于匹配 HLTV 公布的 Stage 1 首轮对阵顺序。",
      "valve 使用 HLTV Valve Global Ranking 2026-05-26 points。",
      "hltv 使用 HLTV World Ranking 2026-05-25 points。",
      "map_stats uses user-provided HLTV past-3-month team map data for the current map_pool: WR, Pick %, Ban %, and W-L.",
      "strength is recalculated with Bayesian WR shrinkage from WR, maps_played, Pick %, and Ban %, then divided by 100 and clamped to [0, 1].",
      "win_rate stores WR as a decimal, maps_played stores wins plus losses, and pick_rate/ban_rate store HLTV percentages as decimals.",
      "Maps with no past-3-month sample or not listed in the source txt are stored as strength=0.0, win_rate=0.0, pick_rate=0.0, ban_rate=1.0, maps_played=0.",
      "First Pick is not treated specially; first-ban priority is inferred from the highest ban_rate, with shared first-ban maps reserved for the lower seed team."
    ]
  },
